+
+- **hdKey Serialization:** ~0.1ms (buffer operations)
+- **Base58Check Encoding:** ~0.5ms (checksum + encoding)
+- **WIF Encoding:** ~0.8ms
+- **Address Generation (HASH160 + Base58Check):** ~0.8ms
